            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Close</span></button>SHOPILOC IS A OPEN-SOURCE PROJECT WITH THE SIMPLE GOAL OF SHOPPERS FINDING LOCAL INDEPENDENT STORES THAT CAN DELIVER TO THEIR HOUSE IN THESE TIMES OF CRISIS.
